checkbox.Text:
Use Mining Drones 
							When checked mining drones will be used instead of combat drones
							
								if ${Script[EVEBot].VariableScope.Config.Miner.UseMiningDrones}
								{
									This:SetChecked
								}
							
							
									Script[EVEBot].VariableScope.Config.Miner:SetUseMiningDrones[${This.Checked}]

